title: Newlyweds Chris & Krystal and Country Artist Matt Stell
description:
Krystal and Chris share details from their “Paradise” wedding, which airs Tuesday, August 27th. Plus, the artist who performed as Krystal walked down the aisle, Matt Stell, calls in.
